---
description: Import path rules — relative imports by default, @src/ absolute imports; @src/ required for src/common and src/lib.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Generally, use relative imports.
- Absolute imports are supported by prefixing with `@src/`.
- For `src/common` and `src/lib`, **always use absolute imports** (e.g. `@src/common/...`, `@src/lib/...`).
